document.full_text: a russian soyuz capsule parachuted onto the kazakh steppe through stiff winds and snow on wednesday, delivering a u.s.-russian astronaut trio to earth after five months on the international space station.
document.title: russian-u.s. soyuz crew lands safely on earth
